---

Locked semantics for the core operators

- Literal: /n  
- Balanced / normalized: /&lt;n/&gt;  
- Pre‑bias / left‑shift: << /n  
- Post‑bias / right‑shift: /n >>  
- Logical inverse / cancellation: /^ acting on the previous /n

